<paragraph id="5847C2BA6746B50CEB963A9340D514BE" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<taxonomicName id="7191CF0E66C6874557E10D9DFDB8E3C3" authority="All." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Achillea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="erba-rotta">
Achillea 
<normalizedToken id="A959DBF8915ACCCDAFC0D58A67C8367A" originalValue="Érba-rótta" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Erba-rotta</normalizedToken>
All.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="EB7392CB7389189C36367350D1A43BA3" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="446F0E622A527C5B5F31775F5BFB0F6B" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Westalpen-Schafgarbe</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="C5810D3707B8A5753B147D416CBFC44C" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" type="description">
<paragraph id="B1F103DB5AD9ECCBF1ED36AC5453F060" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="982DD78B82CE28B0A9264A15419C97EC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Achillea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="moschata">
<emphasis id="53F2632360CB9534FDB0E6EC26FDD647" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">A. moschata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 9) durch folgendes Merkmal: 
<emphasis id="7A384AB39338F2D3B40238209BA9F65E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<normalizedToken id="5ABD0C76A0C1101A5E65AB9815E1C477" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
ungeteilt
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9668AFF45F904ED581625BAC13ECC2F8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">oft nur vorn</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="44E4EE83723359D62D58C5E2EAF49449" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<normalizedToken id="C725327CA8E52C6A1B856069FC1A5C26" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
oder wenig tief fiederteilig
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="AFB654D1732BC1091C0F8E1B015612EE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<normalizedToken id="9D0C92D9531838D909CCE705FD07C5C3" originalValue="geflügelter" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">gefluegelter</normalizedToken>
Mittelnerv so breit oder breiter als die 
<normalizedToken id="7D2FD084708B120E87E3C9B71847868D" originalValue="Länge" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Laenge</normalizedToken>
der Zipfel
</emphasis>
). - 
<normalizedToken id="757DDD4B004F0F4A8486AFE0655F5F35" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="945E1C842FEAC671DB49CEF50CF0F3A3" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis id="8618A401AC7B69A778F623E9E5BA9E56" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="C1399E0CA805416A11CB2731D801BBA8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">18:</emphasis>
Material von den 
<normalizedToken id="022B7E3975F17AF5D2860C9FB7068812" originalValue="französischen" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">franzoesischen</normalizedToken>
Alpen aus Tre Colpas (Favarger 1965).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="78EC629974C0626173B9A0D26C1F6DF6" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis id="BF17CD430018DC37BE338C376840DFD8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin, selten subalpin. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="8794BC4293C1F669DE8F01E6522CE3F9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Achillea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="moschata">
<emphasis id="FCB008651D2BB4D5DD2AA6DDD08146C6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">A. moschata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 9).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EC77DD6EB69AD1D32F0ECC54205E019A" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis id="368210ABAC0F07819B9CEE2AE262C39E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="69A514F4B7899AAEA204C4C1292DB2F9" originalValue="Südwestalpen-Pflanze" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Suedwestalpen-Pflanze</normalizedToken>
:
</emphasis>
Von den Seealpen bis zur Dora Baltea und zum Mont 
<normalizedToken id="23184D92D73C4CAB20C41FAC5DB56C78" originalValue="Iséran" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Iseran</normalizedToken>
. Verbreitungskarte von 
<normalizedToken id="8C1B8B98FDCD8D6040D12D0EFF110064" originalValue="Merxmüller" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Merxmueller</normalizedToken>
(1952). - Im Gebiet: Maurienne, Grajische Alpen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="462D939C21BCC36C8D1EC79C9C8C2B40" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis id="314CA3F4DE8AC431AE99E381AA1B5192" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Die Pflanzen des Aostatals sind tiefer 
<normalizedToken id="BADB15CBEF3C22027BDC38B9F89BD5F6" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
als jene der Seealpen und werden deshalb gelegentlich als 
<emphasis id="CF285DC1474BCAEDEB2CD78CAC5B3924" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">
A. 
<taxonomicName id="1AB1E2F474318EC5FC806A4285E913AA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" form="bezeichnet" genus="Achillea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="morisiana">Morisiana Rchb. f. bezeichnet</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
. Es 
<normalizedToken id="03925D813F0B8773E0A4853E321D616C" originalValue="dürfte" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">duerfte</normalizedToken>
sich um Merkmalsintrogressionen der 
<normalizedToken id="A6CCB0053B140AA579BB8D141FD8C74A" originalValue="nördlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">noerdlich</normalizedToken>
angrenzenden 
<taxonomicName id="304B79930AE0C061D0B468510AFB7371" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Achillea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="561" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="moschata">
<emphasis id="17D6F027ABAEB62C427068F4057FF92A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="561">A. moschata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
handeln.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
